data.description: WELCOME HOME! This charming townhouse has been renovated! Granite countertops in the kitchen and fully renovated master bathroom! All ceramic tile flooring downstairs and wood flooring upstairs. Full sized washer and dryer. This townhome features a spacious living room with lots of natural light. The newer kitchen has a breakfast bar and large dining area that overlooks the private patio oasis. Storage unit off patio.  Great investment. Lease immediately after purchase! This sought after community offers free cable and internet! Gated with security patrol, ample parking, assigned and guest spots. Pets allowed! Close to everything! Only a few minutes to multiple beaches, downtown, Kravis, the airport, I-95, shopping, restaurants, hospitals, night life. This property wont last!
